Package org.universAAL.ui.handler.gui.swing.model Description

The Model contains all the Classes that translate from the IO RDF into Swing components.
Although these classes state what should be shown in each component, the how (fonts, colours, Layouts, etc...) is decided in the Look And feel Package.
See Also:
org.universAAL.ui.handler.gui.swing.defaultLookAndFeel
